{"tid":1800515,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"香港曾經有一座亞洲獨一無二、前衛又富美感的兒童遊樂場。","createTime":"2019-12-28T01:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T03:33:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe14e56e45c11ac1884de85d7463629d3094c9f","tid":1800515,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"今天香港的遊樂場千篇一律、被指欠缺新意和樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n但原來，香港曾經有一座亞洲獨一無二、前衛又富美感的兒童遊樂場。它位於葵涌石籬、華達片場對面，由美國藝術家Paul Selinger設計、皇家香港賽馬會捐助15萬港元動工，1969年建成。<br />\n<br />\n這個公園後來屢次更新、重建，特色設計多年前已消失殆盡，原址即今天的探奇遊樂場和石排街公園。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：青涌生活節及Playgroundology<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGonc7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGonc7f.jpg&h=d9c03fff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kAMjZNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkAMjZNg.jpg&h=88bf5726&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7on7pdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7on7pdX.jpg&h=0311090d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQHCMsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQHCMsi.jpg&h=60953d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ukQm0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ukQm0F.jpg&h=c1969017&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9s7GtFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9s7GtFJ.jpg&h=22b54dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvWPCy6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvWPCy6.jpg&h=280538db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbW10N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbW10N.jpg&h=f48e6870&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oijqaT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoijqaT8.jpg&h=bceb6117&s={SIZE}\"